}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "PCA-2007 A1" is silkscreened on the 5GHz antennas in the FCC photos. The 2.4GHz antennas are integral PCB antennas on the main board.
Default credentials are per the FCC manual and sample label. Referens Camelia? :A D8:EB:97 ('''[[TRENDnet]]''') OUI is presumed to be used based on the manual, but it is (presumably) incorrectly shown as D8:E8:97..
Default SSID formats are assumed based on the FCC sample label. They might be incorrect..
